            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e700">
               <lb ed="#P" n="55"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e796">Boetius de consolatione libro iii capitulo ix</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="56"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e704">Que pestis est efficacior ad nocendum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="57"/>quam familiaris inimicus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e712">
               <lb ed="#P" n="58"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e810">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro primo epistola xxxviii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="59"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e716">illi prudentiores semper sunt qui multorum 
               <lb ed="#P" n="60"/>hominum conuersationibus probantur eruditi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e724">
               <lb ed="#P" n="61"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e822">Ibidem libro xii et fi: epistola iii</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e726">nemo amplius 
               <lb ed="#P" n="62"/>acquirit / quam qui se bona conuersatione tractauerit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e734">
               <pb ed="#P" n="58-v"/>
               <cb ed="#P" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#P" n="1"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e837">Isidorus in sinonomia soliloquiorum libro ii
               <lb ed="#P" n="2"/>capitulo xxx</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e738">Vita malos caue iniquos
               <lb ed="#P" n="3"/>Si fueris socius conuersationis eris / et 
               <lb ed="#P" n="4"/>virtutis. Silis simili coniungi solet / peri<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="5"/>culum 
               est vitam cum malis ducere peritu<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="6"/>losum 
               est vitam cum his qui praue volu<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="7"/>ntatis 
               sunt sociari. Qui tetigerit immundum
               <lb ed="#P" n="8"/>coinquinabitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e755">
               <lb ed="#P" n="9"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e860">Auctor libri qui dicitur facetus capitulo iiii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="10"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e759">Doctior efficitur senior associatus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e765">
               <lb ed="#P" n="11"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e870">Idem capitulo vii</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="12"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e767">Nemo placet stulto nisi dicat quod placet 
               <lb ed="#P" n="13"/>illi. Et malus efficitur qui sociatur ei.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e782">
               <lb ed="#P" n="14"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e890">Auctor rudium doctrine libro ii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="15"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e786">Stulta sequi fatuus consueuit recta pariter
               <lb ed="#P" n="16"/>Conuenienter eos non tenet una domus.
               <lb ed="#P" n="17"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e899">Bernardus de improbatione viciorum capitulo v</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="18"/>Tristis abhorretur nec socialis erit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e798">
               <lb ed="#P" n="19"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e909">Iacobus beneuentanus capitulo iiii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="20"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e802">Qui iacet in ceno non sine sorde manet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e808">
               <lb ed="#P" n="21"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e919">Idem capitulo xxxvii</ref> 
               <lb ed="#P" n="22"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e810">Stat male solus homo solus male va<lb ed="#P" break="no" n="23"/>dit 
               / et ipse / Qui viuit solus / mors sibi 
               <lb ed="#P" n="24"/>vita manet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e818">
               <lb ed="#P" n="25"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e933">Auctor libri qui incipit astrolabi</ref>
               <lb ed="#P" n="26"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e822">Infames fugiat tua conuersatio semper
               <lb ed="#P" n="27"/>Et socio gaude te meliore frui.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-d1e830">
               <lb ed="#P" n="28"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Rd1e946">Prouerbium vulghare</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d29370-Qd1e834">Solo per via andare 
               <lb ed="#P" n="29"/>e folia</quote>
            </p>
